i.	relevant section/regulation;    
ii.	planned compliance improvement actions;  
iii.	how the provider will monitor its own compliance and improvement actions;
iv.	how the provider will ensure that parent complaints are appropriately addressed 
v.	Improvement action taken;  
vi.	date of action taken; and 
vii.	name and signature of person taking action.  
d.	Submit a copy of the compliance improvement plan to the Regulatory Authority on a quarterly basis, commencing on 30 June 2025, with an update on progress.
